  "description": "This individual is an undead human of gaunt frame, with pale skin drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and a noticeably elongated jawline. Gray eyes sit deep in shadowed sockets, fixed in an unblinking stare that emphasizes the absence of living affect. White hair persists in sparse, uneven strands, broken by a broad patch of exposed scalp where the skin has dried and cracked. The hands show hardened, earth-ground staining at the knuckles and nails, consistent with prolonged contact with stone and grave-soil.",
